{
  "category_id": "electrodos",
  "name": "Electrodos",
  "schema_version": "0.1.0-draft",
  "status": "draft",
  "base_unit": "unidad (1 electrodo)",
  "curation_log": [
    "DRAFT generated by the LLM strawman (design §3 step 5) from real corpus samples — cheap and disposable, never authoritative. Requires the full M1 procedure (mining passes, price-discrimination test, expert curation, reference validation) before launch.",
    "Dry run on 50 corpus samples: coverage {'aplicacion': 0.78, 'grupo_etario': 0.32, 'material': 0.12, 'medida': 0.22, 'reutilizable': 0.14}, illegal extractions 0."
  ],
  "attribute_defs": [
    {
      "name": "aplicacion",
      "role": "identity",
      "domain": [
        "desfibrilacion",
        "marcapaso_externo",
        "monitorizacion_ecg",
        "tens",
        "electrocirugia",
        "encefalograma",
        "electrococleografia",
        "cardiaco_implantable"
      ],
      "rules": [
        {
          "kind": "keyword",
          "pattern": "electrococleografia",
          "value": "electrococleografia"
        },
        {
          "kind": "keyword",
          "pattern": "encefalograma|electroencefalograma|\\beeg\\b|copa de oro|\\bcopa\\b",
          "value": "encefalograma"
        },
        {
          "kind": "keyword",
          "pattern": "resincronizacion|seno coronario|epicardico|ventricular|auricular|capsure|\\bis 4\\b|\\bis 1\\b|electrodo introductor",
          "value": "cardiaco_implantable"
        },
        {
          "kind": "keyword",
          "pattern": "\\btens\\b",
          "value": "tens"
        },
        {
          "kind": "keyword",
          "pattern": "electrocirug|electrobicturi|electrobisturi|de corte|asa loop|asa redonda|\\basa\\b|porta electrodo|retorno|paleta|reforzada shaft",
          "value": "electrocirugia"
        },
        {
          "kind": "keyword",
          "pattern": "marcapaso|marcapasos",
          "value": "marcapaso_externo"
        },
        {
          "kind": "keyword",
          "pattern": "desfibrila|\\bdea\\b|cardiolife|lifepak|zoll",
          "value": "desfibrilacion"
        },
        {
          "kind": "keyword",
          "pattern": "monitorizacion|\\becg\\b|punto azul|sensor de frente|impedanciometria|\\bph\\b",
          "value": "monitorizacion_ecg"
        }
      ],
      "curation_notes": "identity: el uso clinico (desfibrilacion, marcapaso, monitorizacion/ECG, TENS, electrocirugia, EEG, electrococleografia, implantable cardiaco) es el discriminador primario de identidad; dominio cerrado por usos observados; reglas ordenadas de especifico a general, marcapaso antes que desfibrilacion porque los parches multifuncionales mencionan ambos."
    },
    {
      "name": "grupo_etario",
      "role": "identity",
      "domain": [
        "adulto",
        "pediatrico",
        "neonatal",
        "recien_nacido",
        "adulto_pediatrico"
      ],
      "rules": [
        {
          "kind": "keyword",
          "pattern": "adulto o pediatric|adulto pediatric|pediatric.{0,10}adulto",
          "value": "adulto_pediatrico"
        },
        {
          "kind": "keyword",
          "pattern": "recien nacido",
          "value": "recien_nacido"
        },
        {
          "kind": "keyword",
          "pattern": "neonatal",
          "value": "neonatal"
        },
        {
          "kind": "keyword",
          "pattern": "pediatric",
          "value": "pediatrico"
        },
        {
          "kind": "keyword",
          "pattern": "adulto",
          "value": "adulto"
        }
      ],
      "curation_notes": "identity: el segmento de paciente distingue productos reales (parche adulto vs pediatrico vs neonatal); valor compuesto adulto_pediatrico para los multifuncionales 2-en-1; regla compuesta primero para no colapsar al primer termino suelto."
    },
    {
      "name": "material",
      "role": "identity",
      "domain": [
        "tela",
        "goma",
        "espuma",
        "oro",
        "metal_cromado"
      ],
      "rules": [
        {
          "kind": "keyword",
          "pattern": "copa de oro|de oro|\\boro\\b",
          "value": "oro"
        },
        {
          "kind": "keyword",
          "pattern": "de tela|\\btela\\b",
          "value": "tela"
        },
        {
          "kind": "keyword",
          "pattern": "de goma|\\bgoma\\b",
          "value": "goma"
        },
        {
          "kind": "keyword",
          "pattern": "espuma",
          "value": "espuma"
        },
        {
          "kind": "keyword",
          "pattern": "cromado",
          "value": "metal_cromado"
        }
      ],
      "curation_notes": "identity: el material del electrodo (tela, goma, espuma, copa de oro, metal cromado) discrimina productos dentro de monitorizacion/EEG; dominio cerrado a materiales observados; ausente en muchas descripciones, pero cuando aparece fija identidad."
    },
    {
      "name": "medida",
      "role": "identity",
      "domain": [
        "5x5cm",
        "5x10cm",
        "10x5cm",
        "3x3cm",
        "36x60mm",
        "25x20mm",
        "20x8mm",
        "13mm",
        "10mm"
      ],
      "rules": [
        {
          "kind": "keyword",
          "pattern": "\\b36\\s*x\\s*60\\b",
          "value": "36x60mm"
        },
        {
          "kind": "keyword",
          "pattern": "\\b25\\s*x\\s*20\\b",
          "value": "25x20mm"
        },
        {
          "kind": "keyword",
          "pattern": "\\b20\\s*x\\s*8\\b",
          "value": "20x8mm"
        },
        {
          "kind": "keyword",
          "pattern": "\\b10\\s*x\\s*5\\b",
          "value": "10x5cm"
        },
        {
          "kind": "keyword",
          "pattern": "\\b5\\s*x\\s*10\\b",
          "value": "5x10cm"
        },
        {
          "kind": "keyword",
          "pattern": "\\b5\\s*x\\s*5\\b",
          "value": "5x5cm"
        },
        {
          "kind": "keyword",
          "pattern": "\\b3\\s*x\\s*3\\b",
          "value": "3x3cm"
        },
        {
          "kind": "keyword",
          "pattern": "\\b13\\s*mm\\b",
          "value": "13mm"
        },
        {
          "kind": "keyword",
          "pattern": "\\b10\\s*mm\\b",
          "value": "10mm"
        }
      ],
      "curation_notes": "identity: el tamano del parche (p.ej. 5x5 vs 10x5 vs 3x3) es identidad real en electrodos TENS/autoadhesivos/monitorizacion; se usan reglas keyword con valor fijo porque la medida lleva dos dimensiones y la regex solo admite un grupo de captura; dominio cerrado a tamanos estandar observados."
    },
    {
      "name": "reutilizable",
      "role": "descriptive",
      "domain": [
        "desechable",
        "reutilizable"
      ],
      "rules": [
        {
          "kind": "keyword",
          "pattern": "reutilizable",
          "value": "reutilizable"
        },
        {
          "kind": "keyword",
          "pattern": "desechable|autoadhesiv",
          "value": "desechable"
        }
      ],
      "curation_notes": "descriptive: se normaliza el ciclo de vida (desechable vs reutilizable) pero no participa en la igualdad porque suele estar implicito en la aplicacion y falta en la mayoria de las descripciones."
    }
  ]
}